  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK196">
<l>payaṉilcoṟ pārāṭṭu vāṉai makaṉeṉaṉ</l>
<l>makkaṭ pataṭi yeṉal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Call not him a man who parades forth his empty words. Call him the chaff of men.</l>
            </lg>
